    "title": "Senior Financial Analyst - Sharekhan Global Group - Multiple Openings",
    "description": "Join the Sharekhan Global Group family as a Senior Financial Analyst in Srinagar. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Sharekhan Global Group:\nSharekhan Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sharekhan Global Group!",
